    EISCO 6PK Wash Bottle for Acetone, 1000ml - Labeled with Color Coded Chemical & Safety Information (4 Colors) - Wide Mouth, Self Venting, Low Density Polyethylene Labs

    Product description

    Our mission is simple; to be TRUSTED by educators, researchers, and scientists throughout the world to design, manufacture, and DELIVER products that allow LEARNING and the development of scientific knowledge.

    For over 50 years, Eisco Scientific has been manufacturing and selling quality science equipment and supplies worldwide. Eisco Scientific is a multinational corporation, providing products to academic and industrial customers in over 100 countries.

    The Eisco Industrial division has been created to focus on the needs of industrial and academic research laboratories. Eisco products have been carefully designed by laboratory professionals along-side experienced engineers with quality and durability in mind. They are manufactured with only the highest grade raw materials and according to international quality standards to ensure that they can withstand use in even the toughest laboratory environments

    Performance plastic with flex ink. Ink won't fade, crack or peel. Each bottle features a two piece construction, consisting of the bottle and leak proof cap with built in nozzle. Features red colored screw cap and nozzle for easy identification.

    Each bottle measures 9" in total height (5.25" bottle alone) & 2.9" diameter. Bottle opening has an inner diameter of 1.7" and an outer diameter measuring 1.9".

    4 Color Coded Chemical Label

    Bottle features four color coded label for Acetone. Easy to read chemical information as well as hazard, safety, and first aid precautionary statements

    Blank Writing Space

    Writable space at the base of the bottle allows user to fill in additional safety information. Flex Ink won't fade, crack or peel.

    Superior LDPE Construction

    Self venting design to eliminate leaks & dripping. Superior quality low density polyethylene (LDPE) construction with long lasting strength. Responsive, with smooth bounce back that won't get stiff over time

    Eisco Labs proudly manufactures its own products using state-of-the-art equipment. Each product is carefully designed by a team of laboratory professionals and experienced engineers with quality and durability in mind. They are manufactured with only the highest grade, raw materials and according to international standards to ensure that they can withstand use in even the toughest laboratory environments.

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    About this Item

    • Six pack Wash Bottles, 1000ml capacity each
    • Easy to read labeling, including chemical information and safety warnings (4 colors)
    • Made of low density polyethylene
    • Self venting design
    • Color coded screw cap for easy identification (4 colors)

    Product Description

    Performance plastic with flex ink. Ink won't fade, crack or peel. Each bottle features a two piece construction, consisting of the bottle and leak proof cap with built in nozzle. The low density polyethylene plastic is very responsive, with smooth bounce back that won't get stiff over time. Easy to control squeeze for dispensing. Pack of 6 wash bottles featuring easy to read labeling and safety warnings. Color code labeled for Acetone (4 colors), with screw cap and nozzle. 1000ml capacity. Self venting. Each bottle measures 10.75" in total height (7" bottle alone) & 3.5" diameter. Bottle opening has an inner diameter of 1.7" and an outer diameter measuring 1.9".
